sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant UI as React Frontend
    participant AuthCtrl as Auth Controller
    participant AuthSvc as Auth Service
    participant UserRepo as User Repository
    participant JwtUtil as JWT Utility
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    
    User->>UI: Enter credentials (Email, Password)
    UI->>AuthCtrl: POST /api/auth/login
    AuthCtrl->>AuthSvc: login(email, password)
    
    AuthSvc->>UserRepo: Find user by email
    UserRepo->>DB: SELECT * FROM users
    DB->>UserRepo: User data
    
    AuthSvc->>AuthSvc: Validate password with BCrypt
    
    alt Password Valid
        AuthSvc->>JwtUtil: generateToken(userDetails)
        JwtUtil->>JwtUtil: Create JWT with<br/>claims & expiration
        JwtUtil->>AuthSvc: Return JWT token
        AuthSvc->>AuthCtrl: AuthResponse(token, user)
        AuthCtrl->>UI: 200 OK {token, user}
        UI->>UI: localStorage.setItem('syncup_token')
        UI->>User: Redirect to Dashboard
    else Password Invalid
        AuthSvc->>AuthCtrl: Throw BadCredentialsException
        AuthCtrl->>UI: 401 Unauthorized
        UI->>User: Show error message
    end
